     H            Y.
      ****************************************************************
      *  PROGRAM    : AFFR18                                         *
      *  WRITTEN    : 03/08/2023                                     *
      *  WRITTEN BY : LEC                                            *
      *  FUNCTION   : UPDATE TOYOTA CANADA BIN SCHEDULE              *
      *               FROM UPLOAD                                    *
      ****************************************************************
     FAFFWP18 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAB#PP80 O   E           K        DISK                      A
      *
     E                    FR         30  4 0
     E                    TO         30  4 0
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      * SYSTEM TIME
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WSDT
     I                                        1   60NOW
     I                                        7  140TODAY
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80YYMMDD
     I                                        1   4 YY
     I                                        5   6 MM
     I                                        7   8 DD
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   40HHMM
     I                                        1   2 HH
     I                                        3   4 MN
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1 120 FR
     I                                        1   40A8FR01
     I                                        5   80A8FR02
     I                                        9  120A8FR03
     I                                       13  160A8FR04
     I                                       17  200A8FR05
     I                                       21  240A8FR06
